{"tid":572357,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HTC全球瘋狂裁員：將退出智慧手機領域！","createTime":"2018-02-25T13:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T18:35:34.000Z","uid":46876,"like":20,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"46d1f289d5e23610fa6fa948f56d3c0f0b0f3d95","tid":572357,"uid":46876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T13:31:55.000Z","msg":"[HTC全球瘋狂裁員：將退出智慧手機領域！]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://china.com.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchina.com.cn&d=mNNUuqySWYqK0AdFYghIRIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=2734e0a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">china.com.cn</a> TW<br />\n<br />\n2018/02/24 09:15<br />\n<br />\n關注<br />\n昔日安卓手機的王者（不少人的第一部安卓手機就是從HTC開始的），現在已經落到了這個情況，真是讓人唏噓啊。<br />\n<br />\n據美國媒體報道稱，手機業務主席張嘉林被裁掉後，HTC美國團隊的大部分成員也被開掉，目前只留下一些負責公司全球事務的員工。<br />\n<br />\n對於裁員一事，HTC對外表示，這主要是加速全球各個區域VR部門與智慧手機部門的合併。<br />\n<br />\n不過事實可沒有他們說的這麼簡單，此舉就是為了徹底退出智慧手機業務。對於現在的HTC來說，旗下手機已經陷入了很尷尬的地位，不但銷量很差，在推新速度上也是越來越慢，當然更別說這部分帶來的盈利了，一直都是賠錢（連續10個季度虧損）。<br />\n<br />\n對於HTC來說，之前他們已經將移動部門的大部分精英打包賣給了穀歌，所以徹底退出手機業務也沒什麼稀奇的吧。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"http://sg.newsrepublic.net/article/i6525924872328053260?user_id=6523447935965856780&amp;language=zh-hant&amp;region=hk&amp;app_id=1239&amp;impr_id=6526483506439129356&amp;gid=6525924872328053260&amp;c=sys&amp;language=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsg.newsrepublic.net%2Farticle%2Fi6525924872328053260%3Fuser_id%3D6523447935965856780%26language%3Dzh-hant%26region%3Dhk%26app_id%3D1239%26impr_id%3D6526483506439129356%26gid%3D6525924872328053260%26c%3Dsys%26language%3Dzh&d=mNNUuqySWYqK0AdFYghIRIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=276e4b23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sg.newsrepublic.net/article/i6525924872328053260?user_id=6523447935965856780&amp;language=zh-hant&amp;region=hk&amp;app_id=1239&amp;impr_id=6526483506439129356&amp;gid=6525924872328053260&amp;c=sys&amp;language=zh</a>"},{"pid":"c377e33b0b99500da550d8e2bb4655d6e33f2d11","tid":572357,"uid":49664,"like":0,